Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我考上的是三流私立大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我总算成为大学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着应该是过着 快乐的大学生活,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字是这么拼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了! 明天我有模拟考!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你,回去念补习班吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#06 春天的冲击!响子的秘密!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为你在打瞌睡 没想到突然站起来大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天有模拟考!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经是大学生了 居然还在作重考生时代的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你的重考生生活 真的很悲惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你醒着吗?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,就算是春天 也不能老是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近每晚都睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会睡不着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,都是管理员不让我睡好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,难道你跟那个美女管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是每天晚上?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在连管理员的手 都还没牵过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么说是她不让你睡好的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每晚都出现在我的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦得正好的时候就醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就半睡半醒的 濛濛眬胧到天亮睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真凄惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至…至少想牵牵她的手!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我已经上了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天到了,樱花也绽放了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有季节改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的完全没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你回来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,因为下午停课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出来散步吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,因为惣一郎缺乏运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这么幽静的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才都没有人经过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱吃那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得我好像被她拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,你也真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,这么说来就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员室的电话从刚才响个不停 会不会是什么重要的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤太郎 惣一郎拜托你照顾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟管理员在一起啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是大学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候你才会记住啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟管理员出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题问得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去了哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一条幽静无人的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜狗散步对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它还有什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些时候我还以为 管理员对你有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果考完试之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本对你不理不睬嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,这对母子真叫人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错 我就知道是你打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期天吗? 好,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么等你来罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有改变的只有你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一之濑太太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话啊,电话 有什么重要的事,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的,下星期天 一刻馆的房东听说要来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?房东?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不知道会不会稍微乖一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,我跟你说 事情不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下星期天房东听说要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年没来的房东特地跑来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说房东要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东到底要来做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房租我都有按时缴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能只是随便来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我们告诉五代一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样 你觉得如何?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有听到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛聚集到我的房间来?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道房东来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是来赶走恶房客的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是要调涨房租 没有必要特地跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是这栋公寓太破旧了 想改建成新大楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题的星期天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一成不变的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一件 宛如被芥末呛到的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是签房租契约时的那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是房东
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少对我来说是个震撼事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么?太没礼貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是房东的女儿啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉其中有阴谋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是来 暗中调查恶房客的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会搬出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里有鬼的人 才会说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临,伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那位重考生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父,我已经是大学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又叫他伯父了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,不要站在这里说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就进去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子也进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用,我在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥陪你玩吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,不要麻烦人家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 听大人讲话也蛮无聊的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,不好意思 麻烦你陪她一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么我们上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么伯父嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天真的到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来气色不错,我放心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这里可以转换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是,因为这里怪人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,一定是这个缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,坐垫给你,还有可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,大哥哥你好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代我向楼下的爸爸问好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的孙女喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷腰不好,所以要我陪他来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说,你是管理员的侄女吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今年几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来有那么成熟吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉蛮成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,管理员她几岁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子婶婶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪到腰了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气变暖和了所以我就很放心 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你出门会不会太勉强了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,你想去见惣一郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,爸爸的腰又痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办? 都已经来到这里了说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不介意的话 让我陪你们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶好耶,跟我们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打扰你们全家团聚 那我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想麻烦一个外人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人?太见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我叫您一声爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你跟他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你别乱说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉,难得的星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婶婶,他好像对我有意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他对我好温柔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是当真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎么亲切 我也不会把孙女嫁给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你出了社会 再来我家正式拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是来扫墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水这样够吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,过去好好祭拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也去上个香好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 毕竟这也是一种缘分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,这是哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我儿子惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得对响子来说真的很残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁过来还不到半年的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才半年的时间 惣一郎就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的到这里就可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的,上坡之后还要回转 很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人如果还活着 或许会渐渐发现很多缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,死去的人是天下无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且,只在一起生活半年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间的回忆在她内心 逐渐扩大成为她的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:23:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,千万不能逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的惣一郎已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会变成一个好男人 保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好地往前看,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着前方向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地看着前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,走路要看着前方才行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的名字叫惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他永远活在我的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 ‘五代烦恼不已!响子喜欢的人’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎 和你一起度过的快乐时光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:06.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:43.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}光只是眨个眼 就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:25:06.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}明明已经可以相爱 偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:18.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}我快要忍受不了 快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}真是痛苦的折磨

